  <brief_title>Intrapleural Bevacizumab and Cisplatin Therapy for Malignant Pleural Effusion Caused by Non-small Cell Lung Cancer</brief_title>
  <official_title>Open-labeled, Randomized, Multicenter Phase III Study of Adjuvant Chemotherapy Comparing Bevacizumab Plus Cisplatin With Cisplatin Regimen in Malignant Pleural Effusion of Advanced Stage Non-Small-Cell Lung Cancer Patients</official_title>
