  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To determine the efficacy and Safety of intrapleural Bevacizumab and cisplatin as a treatment
      for malignant pleural effusions (MPE) in patients with non-small cell lung cancer (NSCLC).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
